==Awards and nominations==
==Box-office ranking==
For a number of years, exhibitors voted Holden among the most popular stars in the country:
* 1954 – 7th (US)
* 1955 – 4th (US)
* 1956 – 1st (US)
* 1957 – 7th (US)
* 1958 – 6th (US), 6th (UK)
* 1959 – 12th (US)
* 1960 – 14th (US)
* 1961 – 8th (US)
* 1962 – 15th (US)

